Resilience was created with Fabienne Bouvier and Chloé Leroux as a school project, and was exhibited at the Centre d&rsquo;Arts d&rsquo;Enghien-les-Bains.
The project takes the form of a virtual exhibition of a fictive artist. Each artwork can be interacted with to reveal traces and echoes of the artist&rsquo;s life — fragments of memory, emotion, and identity embedded in the work itself.
